    &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; alt=&#34;EasyFlatpak&#34; src=&#34;https://i.imgur.com/xTVwNVj.png&#34;&gt;

  
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

